text: Judgment Day (2009) was a professional wrestling pay-per-view show made by World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE). It took place on May 17, 2009 at the Allstate Arena in Rosemont, Illinois, a suburb of Chicago. It was the eleventh and last Judgment Day event held by WWE, as Judgment Day was replaced by Over the Limit in 2010. ==Results== ==Related pages== *List of WWE pay-per-view events ==References== ==Other websites== *The official Judgment Day website Category:WWE Judgment Day Category:Sports in Chicago Category:2009 in professional wrestling Category:2009 in Illinois Category:May 2009 events
